constraints_details.result: Hinterland Lower Lea Valley including Stratford

description: Demolition of 1,187.5sqm GIA of existing buildings and yard space comprising 278.2sqm Class B1, 220.4sqm Class B2 and 688.9sqm Sui Generis. Redevelopment of a mixed use scheme totalling 18,329sqm GIA floorspace comprising 175 residential units (14,848sqm) (Class C3), 2,503sqm employment space comprising 1,648sqm Class B1, 221sqm Class B2, and 345sqm commercial use (Class A1/A3) plus 289sqm of ancillary spaces, 660sqm on plot lower ground floor parking alongside 3,951sqm public realm, open space and associated vehicular access.
